      ],
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content-image-block.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Learn About Your Device",
        "text": "<h2>Learn About Your Device</h2><p>Qure's Micro-Infusion device uses 24K gold plated needles to deliver concentrated serum directly below the surface of your skin.</p><p>The needles are thinner than a strand of hair, so the treatment feels gentle — but the results are powerful.</p><p>[image]</p><p><strong>It works in two ways:</strong></p><ol><li>It triggers your skin's natural repair response for smoother and firmer looking skin.</li><li>It creates tiny, invisible channels in the surface of your skin, allowing powerful active ingredients to absorb deeper and work faster.</li></ol>"
      }
    },
